{"tid":932363,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"都怪long d既錯","createTime":"2018-12-07T16:32:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T17:22:35.000Z","uid":211425,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"972ac9e5db8cec1fea3daea99220e76ea7b5e17c","tid":932363,"uid":211425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T16:32:23.000Z","msg":"暑假個時見返小學識既男仔 之後大家鐘意大家 但keep左兩個禮拜佢就要飛返外國讀書 所以無話一齊 但做既野同情侶差唔多 <br />\n佢飛左過去一個月都keep到 但之後佢就話忙 唔得閒 開始一星期先覆一兩句 直到今朝早佢同我講清楚 話 佢其實已經無咁鐘意我  所以先一直逃避話忙 唔搵唔理 佢亦都無諗過我可以long d 以為唔理我幾個月我自己就會走 <br />\n最後佢話 當初佢真係好愛我 唔係玩我 所以佢叫我揀 佢覆點做先令我過得舒服d (姐係隨緣見，固定圈子聚會，永唔見)我叫佢幫我揀 佢諗左陣 話固定圈子見<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得佢係啱既人 所以唔想放手 但無奈我無得揀 只可以順住佢劇本走"},{"pid":"b94f8ef67a4c8a0187bf348fadd8c2a19585e81b","tid":932363,"uid":1249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T16:45:40.000Z","msg":"long e呢"},{"pid":"c10f133cdfb7fed98793ef0826e57757638155d8","tid":932363,"uid":109933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T17:06:29.000Z","msg":"你覺得佢啱你<br />\n但人地覺得你唔啱佢啊嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd461e7245f351f14f35023583ccb89a0eb0f93a","tid":932363,"uid":211425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c10f133cdfb7fed98793ef0826e57757638155d8","tid":932363,"uid":109933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T17:06:29.000Z","msg":"你覺得佢啱你<br />\n但人地覺得你唔啱佢啊嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T17:22:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我知呀"},{"pid":"3242d3a6491e70266845ae849e75247c0f438c4a","tid":932363,"uid":211425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b94f8ef67a4c8a0187bf348fadd8c2a19585e81b","tid":932363,"uid":1249,"like":1,"disl